				<p>
					Enhanced foundation logic: Introducing new <code>UserService</code> to provide a consistent user management.
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="https://sourceforge.net/apps/mantisbt/josceleton/view.php?id=15">#0000015</a> 
